12 Mar 2015Media accreditation for the reburial of Moses Kotane and JB Marks will no longer be live (no photographs will be taken). Members of the media whose accreditation applications have been approved are requested to collect their accreditations between 12h00 Thursday, 12 March and 08h00 Saturday,14 March 2015. The venue is Pella Tribal Administration Office near the Post Office. For accreditation related queries contact: Ishmael Selemale Contact: 0617905114 or Obed Makgoale Contact: 060 974 0789Media enquiries: Sandile Memela Contact: 0828003750 Email: SandileM@dac.gov.zaIssued by the Department of Communications